 *
 *   pin name           pin number
 *   -----------------------------
 *   I2C_6_SDA       112
 *   I2C_6_SCL       111
 *
 * In Linux you need to set CONFIG_SERIAL_SC16IS7XX_CORE=y (or m) to be able to use
